title: Kylie Minogue at iTunes Festival London 2014 HD 720p.mp4
description: Ms Minogue returns in all her ever-smiling, costume-changing, high-gloss pop glory, drawing on a hefty back catalogue that runs the gamut from the genuinely great ('Can't Get You Out of My Head') to the old faves ('The Locomotion'), but chiefly promoting her poptastic new record 'Kiss Me Once'. Party-starting pop prince MNEK backs Kylie up in the support slot.
